  <!--Header-Area-->

  <header class="blue-bg relative fix" id="home">
      <div class="section-bg overlay-bg angle-bg ripple ">
          <div id="home-parallax-image">
            <%= image_tag("header-bg2.jpg", class: "offset-bg")  %>
          </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-100"></div>
      <div class="space-20 hidden-xs"></div>
      <!--Header-Text-->
      <div class="container text-white">
          <div class="row text-center">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 col-md-12">
                  <div class="space-40"></div>
                  <div class="space-100 d-sm-none"></div>
                  <h1>Helping you navigate your chronic care journey</h1>
                  <div class="space-20"></div>
                  <!-- search bar -->
                  <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
                    <form id="mc-form" class="subscrie-form">
                        <label class="mt10" for="mc-email"></label>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="What can we help you find today?">
                            <div class="input-group-btn">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">
                                  <span class="ti-search"></span>
                                  Search</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                  </div>

                  <div class="space-100"></div>
                  <div class="space-100 d-sm-none"></div>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-80"></div>
      </div>
      <!--Header-Text/-->
  </header>
  <!--Header-Area/-->
  <section>
      <div class="space-60"></div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row wow fadeInUp">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 text-center">
                <h3>Sign up today for FREE access to personalized tools to help you on your care journey.</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
          <div class="row">
              <div class="space-60"></div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                  <div id="tinted-image1" class="well well-hover text-center">
                      <% if user_signed_in? %>
                        <%= link_to dashboard_plan_path do %>
                        <p class="md-icon"><span class="ti-agenda" style="color: #B580D1"></span></p>
                        <% end %>
                      <% else %>
                        <%= link_to plan_path do %>
                        <p class="md-icon"><span class="ti-agenda" style="color: #B580D1"></span></p>
                        <% end %>
                      <% end %>
                      <div class="space-10"></div>
                      <h5>
                        <% if user_signed_in? %>
                          <%= link_to "Helping you organize your care needs", dashboard_plan_path %>
                        <% else %>
                          <%= link_to "Helping you organize your care needs", plan_path %>
                        <% end %>
                      </h5>
                      <p>Keeping track of all your appointments, medications, and relevant information should be easier. Our tools can help you stay organized.</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
                  <div id="tinted-image2" class="well well-hover text-center">
                      <% if user_signed_in? %>
                        <%= link_to symptoms_path do %>
                        <p class="md-icon"><span class="ti-target" style="color: #41B6E6"></span></p>
                        <% end %>
                      <% else %>
                        <%= link_to track_path do %>
                        <p class="md-icon"><span class="ti-target" style="color: #41B6E6"></span></p>
                        <% end %>
                      <% end %>
                      <div class="space-10"></div>
                      <h5>
                        <% if user_signed_in? %>
                          <%= link_to "Things I'm tracking", symptoms_path %>
                        <% else %>
                          <%= link_to "Things I'm tracking", track_path %>
                        <% end %>
                      </h5>
                      <p>A big part of managing your day-to-day chronic care needs is self-tracking. Our visualizations of your data might provide new insight into making those days the best they can be within your context.</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
                  <div id="tinted-image3" class="well well-hover text-center">
                      <% if user_signed_in? %>
                        <%= link_to dashboard_goals_path do %>
                        <p class="md-icon"><span class="ti-cup" style="color: #E06287"></span></p>
                        <% end %>
                      <% else %>
                        <%= link_to goal_centre_path do %>
                        <p class="md-icon"><span class="ti-cup" style="color: #E06287"></span></p>
                        <% end %>
                      <% end %>
                      <div class="space-10"></div>
                      <h5>
                        <% if user_signed_in? %>
                          <%= link_to "Set and Manage your goals", dashboard_goals_path %>
                        <% else %>
                          <%= link_to "Set and Manage your goals", goal_centre_path %>
                        <% end %>
                      </h5>
                      <p>Setting SMART goals is a great way to successfully get to where you want to be. We’ve put together a guided step-by-step guides to help you reach your goals.</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-80"></div>
  </section>
  <!--Work-Section-->
  <section class="gray-bg" id="work">
      <div class="space-80"></div>
      <div class="container">
          <div class="row wow fadeInUp">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-center">
                  <h3 class="text-uppercase">How it works</h3>
                  <p>Managing long term health care needs can feel overwhelming or like a full time job at times. We’re building tools for patients just like you to make that job just a little bit easier.</p>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-60"></div>
          <div class="row">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 text-center wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                  <div class="hover-shadow">
                      <div class="space-60">
                          <%= image_tag ("icon/icon5.png") %>
                      </div>
                      <div class="space-20"></div>
                      <h5 class="text-uppercase">We Talked to Patients Like You</h5>
                      <p>We listened to groups of patients with (sometimes multiple) chronic conditions to find out what challenges and issues they deal with on a day-to-day basis.</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 text-center wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
                  <div class="hover-shadow">
                      <div class="space-60">
                          <%= image_tag("icon/icon1.png") %>
                      </div>
                      <div class="space-20"></div>
                      <h5 class="text-uppercase">We Met with Care Providers</h5>
                      <p>We also talked to health care providers to understand their perspectives on those same challenges and issues.</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 text-center wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
                  <div class="hover-shadow">
                      <div class="space-60">
                          <%= image_tag("icon/icon2.png") %>
                      </div>
                      <div class="space-20"></div>
                      <h5 class="text-uppercase">We Worked with Designers and Developers</h5>
                      <p>Together with a group of forward-thinking Canadian developers, we’re building a suite of tools and supports to make your job easier.</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3 text-center wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.8s">
                  <div class="hover-shadow">
                      <div class="space-60">
                          <%= image_tag("icon/icon4.png") %>
                      </div>
                      <div class="space-20"></div>
                      <h5 class="text-uppercase">Our Vision</h5>
                      <p>Our vision is for these tools to become part of a seamless ecosystem where you and your care providers can work together to make living with chronic care needs easier for all you and everyone who helps you on that journey.</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-60"></div>
          <div class="row">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center wow fadeInUp">
                  <div class="up-offset ">
                      <%= image_tag("home-feat1.jpg") %>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>
